FBIS4-16591 "drsov074_o_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 Uzbekistan Russian Ruble Outlawed in Uzbekistan From 15 Apr Russian Ruble Outlawed in Uzbekistan From 15 Apr LD1504092394 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0330 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504092394 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] From today the circulation of Russian bank notes is prohibited on the territory of Uzbekistan. The government resolution on this has been signed by Uzbek President Islam Karimov. From today the exchange rate of the som, that is of the coupon to analogous foreign currencies, will be determined during regular trading at the Uzbek republican currency exchange.
